dc_description_s: These polygon and point data layers represent parks for Green County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Green_Parks_2017.gdb. The features included in the geodatabase are 'GREEN_PARKS_UNK_PNT' and 'GREEN_PARKS_UNK_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.greencountywi.org/179/Downloadable-GIS-Data-Forms
